Through this scholarship, we aim to encourage women to excel in computing
and technology and become active role models and leaders in their
communities. Below are the details:

   -

   Female engineering students will be will be chosen from bachelor=E2=80=
=99s,
   master=E2=80=99s and PhD programs. Please read through the eligibility c=
riteria and
   application form in detail here
   <https://google.eresources.com/applications/default.asp>
   -

   All scholarship recipients, chosen from the applicant pool across
   Australia, New Zealand, Japan, Korea, Southeast Asia and India, will be
   invited to attend the annual scholars retreat at Google Hyderabad
between August
   30th to September 2nd, 2016. Their travel and stay will be sponsored by
   us
   -

   Recipients of the scholarship will receive a scholarship amount specific
   to their local region in respect to tuition (Rs. 1,00,000 per student in
   India).
   -

   The deadline to apply for the scholarship is May 8th, 2016

We would request you to share this with all female students at the
earliest. Students can reach out to me in case of any questions.

Looking forward to a huge participation from your institute!




